additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Not to be used for any purpose, or in any manner, contrary to this label unless authorised. Keep out of reach of children. Flammable until dry. Do not store or use near naked flame. Do not spray directly on exposed food, food preparation surfaces or food utensils. If swallowed, seek medical advice. If rash or irritation occurs discontinue use. If poisoning occurs, contact a doctor or Poisons Information Centre. Phone Australia 13 11 26. Phone New Zealand 0800 764 766.
